   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Copy  for the northern ktema, Pauni 21 of the 12th indiction.;(Cross) Account of the 100 knidia and the 61 keramia of wine as follows:;to the steward: 54 keramia of wine;;for the expenses of transport: 2 keramia of wine;;for a fraction: 3 keramia of wine;;for the soldiers: 2 keramia of wine.;Makes 61 keramia of wine.;(And) as follows:;96 small vessels;;for the expenses of tranport: 2 vessels;;for a fraction: 2 vessels.;Makes 100 vessels of wine.</ab>
         </div>
